Dialogue: 1,1:17:38.80,1:17:41.05,CN,,0,0,0,,檢索 選出
Dialogue: 0,1:17:41.72,1:17:42.59,JP,,0,0,0,,解析
Dialogue: 1,1:17:41.72,1:17:42.59,CN,,0,0,0,,解析
