Dialogue: 1,1:17:47.85,1:17:51.10,CN,,0,0,0,,吾身為劍所鑄
Dialogue: 0,1:17:53.69,1:17:54.77,JP,,0,0,0,,ロー
Dialogue: 1,1:17:53.69,1:17:54.77,CN,,0,0,0,,熾天覆…
